{"tid":1365759,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"727李鵬悼念會小小心意","createTime":"2019-07-25T17:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T11:18:38.000Z","uid":288912,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ac4a508f05fb19ea2f0f61c69a07fb8dde3fcf4d","tid":1365759,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:43:17.000Z","msg":"適逢元朗國發出不反對通知書、反而特區發反對通知書，參考幾篇元朗人意見，覺得可以咁樣：<br />\n<br />\n1）高呼「支持李鵬屠城、支持警察鄉黑、<span style=\"color: red;\">支持非法政權</span>」，唔排除有睇唔過眼嗌「反對恐怖主義，撤查元朗暴動」<br />\n2）去元朗警署要求警察承認自己係中國人、支持屠殺平民，唔排除有人睇唔過眼嗌「交出恐怖份子」<br />\n3）悼念會需要香港護衛，保障人身安全。護衛應該係無組織、自發嘅小隊，好似first aid咁<span style=\"color: red;\">不受《社團條例》打壓</span>。宗旨係「制服所有<span style=\"color: red;\">不平等武力</span>」，而唔係制服自衛反抗。保護對象切記係<strong>所有</strong>「手無寸鐵嘅市民」，而唔係保護<strong>任何</strong>有槍炮有權力嘅人。要慢慢建立自衛武力嘅依據<br />\n<br />\n歡迎提出其他悼念方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccd7e8fd5a2dcf3941d76c48775c9a4c5e5c8c8b","tid":1365759,"uid":137053,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:17:25.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家真係要自己預備好需要嘅裝備啊，唔好成日發夢都靠現場有人俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如基本裝：頭盔、眼罩、豬咀<br />\n<br />\n用完又隨手抌咗佢，次次發完夢都見到有啲好新淨嘅裝被丟，好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝咁多個為香港仆心仆命嘅香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df862de947bcf18d1f23a5abd912913b60c4ee91","tid":1365759,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccd7e8fd5a2dcf3941d76c48775c9a4c5e5c8c8b","tid":1365759,"uid":137053,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:17:25.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\